<TEXT>
the british government says its a gun but 
speculation rages about iraqs purpose in ordering eight massive 
steel tubes that were seized by british customs officers 
whatever device the tubes may have been for it would be the 
worlds largest perhaps a cannon a rocket launcher an update of 
