revolution has tree planting become so trendy 
a tree planted today can enrich the lives of generations yet 
unborn president bush said march 22 when he planted an eastern 
red bud on the white house lawn so let us plant the trees and 
nurture them so that america will remain america the beautiful for 
generations to come 
bush then mused that john quincy adams planted am elm on the 
